sys_script_include.description:
Dev request state constants, use these constants when determining which state to use.

Example - is the dev request in the "In Development" state:
var devGr = new GlideRecord("x_wms_pulse.dev_request");
if (devGr.get("[sys_id]") && devGr.state == DevRequestStates.IN_DEVELOPMENT)
    // do something when the dev request is in development

Example 2 - change an dev request state to "Done"
var devGr = new GlideRecord("x_wms_pulse.dev_request");
if (devGr.get("[sys_id]"))
    devGr.state = DevRequestStates.DONE
devGr.update();

sys_script_include.script:
